Package: zoteror
Title: Allows to interact with zotero to add citations and create bibtex file
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("BenoÃ®t", "Depaire", email = "benoit@depaire.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows you to interact with Zotero to automagically add citations in your Markdown documents and to generate a corresponding bibtex file. This plugin requires that Zotero is running and you have installed the 'Zotero Better Bib(la)tex' add-on in Zotero.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
